From edd at debian.org  Tue Mar 18 12:35:39 2014
From: edd at debian.org (Dirk Eddelbuettel)
Date: Tue, 18 Mar 2014 06:35:39 -0500
Subject: [Rcpp-devel] Building shared libs with Rcpp does not work as
 before after Debian update
